Part of Charles-Hubert's premium collection, the Charles-Hubert, Paris Stainless Steel Two-Tone Mechanical Pocket Watch #3553-T is a precision crafted timepiece with 17-jewel winding movement, skeletal display, and white dial with 24 hour sun and moon subdial. Made of 14K gold-plated stainless steel for lasting beauty and durability, this watch features black-tone Arabic numerals, black-tone hands, seconds subdial on the inner dial, and engraved black-tone Roman numerals on the gold-tone back cover. Elegant and contemporary, this watch arrives in a deluxe blue giftbox with matching curb chain.
